Products.RichDescription:
L'Or Espresso Estremo Intensity 10 is a spicy, powerful and daring ground coffee in capsules. Compatible with Nespresso* coffee machines.

A daring blend, Lungo Estremo is a mystical ride through the tantalizing aroma of dark roasted espresso, intensified by spicy notes to achieve a powerful and full-bodied coffee experience inspired by extremes.

Flavours: Spicy, powerful, daring

Intensity: 10

Ideal Preparation: 110mL Lungo

*Trademark used is of a third party not related to Jacobs Douwe Egberts.

Products.RichDescription:
Country Life Bakery Gluten Free Bread White is great for sandwiches.

Introducing our ever gluten free recipe!

Since 1984, Country Life Bakery has been passionately committed to baking the best-tasting gluten free bread so that you can enjoy every slice.

Our bakers have been working on a new recipe ... our super soft, most delicious gluten free bread with generous-sized slices that are perfect for sandwiches and toast!

With tasty, bigger slices you'll be amazed it's gluten free, but don't worry - it is!

New deliciously recipe.

- Source of fibre.

- No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

- Baked in Australia.

Dairy free.

Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Stevia Sweet Liquid With Agave' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
SteviaSweet Liquid with Agave with 100% natural sweetness.

Enjoy the great tasting 100% Natural low calorie sweetness in SteviaSweet which comes from the leaves of the stevia plant, combined with other natural ingredients.

SteviaSweet Liquid with Agave is the clever new way to sweeten your food and drinks naturally, with each 0.5mL serve (10 drops) providing the same amount of sweetness as a teaspoon of sugar. Just 0.67kJ (0.16 kcalories) per serve of SteviaSweet Liquid compared to 70kJ (16.7 kcalories) per teaspoon of sugar for the same amount of sweetness! SteviaSweet Liquid is also heat stable, so its perfect for cooking and baking, and for using in hot drinks, as well as in cold drinks like smoothies, and to sweeten desserts and yogurt.?
SteviaSweet Liquid with Agave is made in Switzerland, and is Vegan, Gluten Free, and Kosher.

10 drops (0.5mL) of SteviaSweet Liquid with Agave provides the same amount of sweetness as 1 teapoon of sugar, and 25ml of of SteviaSweet Liquid with Agave provides the same amount of sweetness as 1 cup of sugar.

SteviaSweet Liquid with Agave is also great value with 250 serves per bottle, and the easy-to-use squeeze bottle has a nozzle to let you dispense one drop at a time.
